cvd_grid                Create a grid of different color-deficiency
                        simulations of a plot
edit_colors             Edit colors in existing plot or grid object
gg_color_gradient       Generate a continuous color gradient to be
                        colored via ggplot2's 'scale_fill_*' mechanism
gg_color_swatches       Generate a set of color swatches to be colored
                        via ggplot2's 'scale_fill_*' mechanism
palette_OkabeIto        Color palette proposed by Okabe and Ito
palette_plot            Visualize a color palette as swatches of
                        colors, possibly with labels printed on top
scale_colour_OkabeIto   Okabe-Ito color scale
view_cvd                Interactively view cvd simulations of a figure
                        or plot
